        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">i'm not talking like raids on derv 3 where you zerg dorn, i mean end game raids. What's your guild's policy on pets on raids?  what do you think about it?</P><P>here i'll go first. I'm unguilded, but the last 4 guilds that i raided with didn't allow pets. They also failed while the mob was at 5% health, which would have been dead if it was because of pets. I would assume that anyone guilded in these guilds is not a complete idiot, and therefor could control thier pets</P><P>I think that the damage and tanking ability, albeit only for short times, would benefit just about any encounter. Maybe there's something i'm not understanding about it, plese enlighten me.</P><P><img src="http://www.manifest-angel.com/syrox/reaper.jpg" border=0></P><P>"And Syrox, fix your damn sig too."<BR>Niygor the Malevolent<BR></font></td>
