        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">We always use pets. We're not the highest end out there, but we kill stuff like Velk / Kunark dragons / Wuoshi / Zlandikar. We would kill Statue/Vindic if we could get our clerics to log at the same time. </P><P>Pets are hardly ever a casualty on boss mobs, they're a problem in some dungeons, that's about it. </P><P>Fearable pets are a problem when there's fear (but usually outside it's no big deal), so you might limit pre-59 mages/necro pets. </P><P>Now that 55+ mobs' corpses can't poof anymore, there's absolutely no reason to forbid them.  </P><P>Just have people summon the pets on the spot (and not drag them all the way from the zone line).</P><P><img src="http://www.lesgensdici.com/~nico/ampimp.jpg" border=0><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
