        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Our spectre pets are pretty much useless against Super bosses that does massive AoE.<BR>On the other hand Boss against like tormax,Vindi,statue, pets are very effective.</P><P>Here is  some pointers</P><P>1.use /pet no taunt<BR>2.always buff pet<BR>3.send in pet after main tanks get agro<BR>4./pet back off after mob ENRAGE. </P><P>Our guild once parsed melee damage for tormax. Top Rogue with vulak weapon made 25k damage, our pet made 6k damage. Not too bad as free dmg dealer. ( and you can land most dots on himself too)</P><P>I do not summon pets against most TOVN dragons. (except Vyemm,Aary). Other than those I summon pets for boss.</P><P>For Lord yelinak we ask clerics to Aego <img src=icon_smile_big.gif border=0 align=middle> pets and they last whole fight.</P><P></P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=13609" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=13609</a><BR><p><BR><img border="0" src="http://members.aol.com/ivyeni/brownivysig3-1.jpg"></p></P><P><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
