        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Pets are only useful on single target raids on those single targets as long as they can last a few AoEs and don't get feared all over the zone.  They are never allowed on general zone raids like Hate and Fear (in my experiance) because it's often times hard to keep them off the mobs if you get aggroed on a large pull.  I can see pets sometimes used on such raids if you're level 59+, have pet discipline, the zone dosn't have crappy pathing and your pet won't get feared all over the zone (mages and necros).</P><P>But yeah, on single targets that won't own the pets right away in a big AoE, I almost always see pets being used.</P><P>Reegor Mortees<BR>57th necro<BR>E'Ci<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
